          <attvalue for="4" value="0.8" />
          <attvalue for="5" value="Alan Turing: The Enigma (1983) is a biography of the British mathematician, codebreaker, and early computer scientist, Alan Turing (1912–1954) by Andrew Hodges." />
          <attvalue for="6" value="" />
